{"lastModified":1773239855136,"uri":"c::18633696598::vessel::7ee88ff0-b30a-11ef-9263-5385f90779b2","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Indonesia\n\nThe Jinggo Janggo Phinisi presents a perfect choice for a family cruise or lovely honeymooners amidst the breathtaking beauty of Indonesia. This vessel boasts a deck space perfect for resting in between engaging activities. Inside, it houses two comfortable cabins with a shared bathroom, ensuring a relaxing and enjoyable journey.\n\nEmbarking on the Jinggo Janggo boat offers a captivating exploration of the renowned Komodo National Park and the enchanting nearby islands. Departing from Labuan Bajo, the itineraries are thoughtfully crafted, catering to individual preferences and spanning up to 7-nights of unforgettable experiences.\n\nEager to provide unforgettable adventures, the Jinggo Janggo is fully equipped to indulge in a wide range of activities, be it the enchanting depths of scuba diving, invigorating treks, mesmerizing snorkeling, or simply venturing into the hidden gems of remote beaches.\n\nThe Jinggo Janggo liveaboard boasts two appointed double cabins, one thoughtfully designed to accommodate an extra single bed. This thoughtful arrangement renders it a perfect for either four adults and one child or a group of five adults. With extra bedding on deck, embracing the outdoors for a starlit sleep becomes even more inviting. A cozy setup under the stars awaits, blending comfort and nature’s serenity. An opportunity to slumber surrounded by the night’s enchantment. With its versatility, the Jinggo Janggo offers a truly delightful and comfortable stay for diverse group compositions.","blueprint":{"name":"JINGGO JANGGA","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::7ee88ff0-b30a-11ef-9263-5385f90779b2::assets::6b91e6e0-b30f-11ef-9b9b-adbf406beac5/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::7ee88ff0-b30a-11ef-9263-5385f90779b2::assets::6b8c1a80-b30f-11ef-9b9b-adbf406beac5/{imageVariant}","/media